สำหรับ Advance Events แบ่งออกเป็น 2 Sets ใหญ่ๆ

1. ***General Purpose:***
	* `Link` – event triggers that break long sequence flows.
	* `Multiple` – a combination of event triggers, any one of which will trigger the event.
	* `Parallel multiple` – a combination of event triggers, all of which are required to trigger the event.

2. ***Errors:***               
	* `Error events` – error handling using a simple throw/catch paradigm.     
	* `Escalation events` – deferring responsibility to a higher level of authority.    
	* `Compensation events` – undoing completed activities after an error.     
	* `Cancel events` – canceling all or nothing transactions.